{
  "stem": "25114.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They had such big propaganda in the Soviet Union about how mighty they were, and they were showing it on the streets-- the marching and the tanks and everything.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, for a moment, I was happy-- that they attacked there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, now the Soviet Union will push-- throw out the Germans from Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We'll be back to family.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We will reunite.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was my first reaction, because I was so positive that the-- how could Germans, who were at war with so many countries, attack such a might as the Soviet Union and not be pushed back?",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, sadly, that wasn't the case.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In about three days, they engaged, and they took us-- they assembled us and the things.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They said everybody's going to contribute to the war effort.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "First we went to a big hall in the city, and we sat all night, writing conscription for the enlistment-- letters for the all-- people who were-- uh-- for-- how do you call it?",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Who need to go to the war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Conscription.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Conscription letters-- conscript-- so we sat all night and wrote all those conscriptions letter--",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Huh?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The whole school, almost everybody, you see, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We've got to start from somewhere.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they said, we'll go to this hall, and we'll take the list of all the people at this particular age group, and we'll pick them out from the list of citizens and send them letters.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we wrote those letters and filled those out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then we were trying to-- in our college, it was the end of the year, so we're trying to convert it to a hospital.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we helped there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then, all of a sudden, they were running.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The Russian army was running.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
